title: Ancylosis ormuzdella
text: Ancylosis ormuzdella is a species of <a href="Pyralidae">snout moth</a> in the genus "<a href="Ancylosis">Ancylosis</a>". It was described by <a href="Hans%20Georg%20Amsel">Hans Georg Amsel</a> in 1954, and is known from <a href="Shiraz">Shiraz</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>.
